# permissions.json Template

> Reference: `docs/principles/permissions-as-design.md`
> Adjust paths to match your kb/ structure.

Restrictive diagnostic archetype:
- read: allow (deny .env, .ssh)
- write: deny default; allow kb/active/, tmp/
- bash: deny default; allow bin/*, scoped git
- grep/find/ls: deny (forces index navigation)

Pair every skill `allowed-tools` bash pattern with an allow entry here.
